{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-art-post-js","path":"/machine/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"I built a drawing machine which successfully painted my first self-portrait ( test experiment )","html":"<p>I built a drawing machine which successfully painted my first self-portrait ( test experiment )</p>\n<p>我嘗試獨立搭建一個繪圖機器的原型，並完成第一幅以機器作為媒材的「自畫」像。使用上，只要輸入一張圖片，機器就能將畫筆定位在指定的位置並繪製想要的圖案。機械架構用的是CNC三軸定位座標(2個步進馬達＋1個伺服馬達)，並搭配Gcode作為軟體控制。此外，在這些初步嘗試後，希望能讓機器對圖像有更深層的認知 (AI)，探索人類與機器共同協作的更多可能性。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Drawing machine","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3953900709219857,"src":"/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/32ee9/machine.jpg","srcSet":"/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/0aa4b/machine.jpg 125w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/4d406/machine.jpg 250w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/32ee9/machine.jpg 500w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/9f583/machine.jpg 750w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/2f7e7/machine.jpg 1000w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/534dc/machine.jpg 3148w","sizes":"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/machine/"}}}